00:50:06.960 --> 00:50:10.920
The problem is it's
largely unconscious.

00:50:10.920 --> 00:50:15.050
It's unconscious bias
of the worse sort.

00:50:15.050 --> 00:50:17.500
People just-- in
any area you look

00:50:17.500 --> 00:50:23.480
at, education, Syria, housing,
interest rates, economic income

00:50:23.480 --> 00:50:25.510
distribution, et cetera,
there's the questions

00:50:25.510 --> 00:50:27.240
you're allowed to
ask and the questions

00:50:27.240 --> 00:50:30.290
that sound a bit weird.

00:50:30.290 --> 00:50:31.790
And I've been on
news programs where

00:50:31.790 --> 00:50:35.220
I've raised a weird question and
boy do they get you out fast.

00:50:35.220 --> 00:50:37.690
It's like, oh, what's this
question you're asking?

00:50:37.690 --> 00:50:40.602
We thought you were coming to
talk about classroom sizes.

00:50:40.602 --> 00:50:43.060
And now you're starting to talk
about what education is for

00:50:43.060 --> 00:50:44.670
and what learning is about.

00:50:44.670 --> 00:50:45.890
Off the stage.

00:50:45.890 --> 00:50:48.155
There's censorship of
this kind of thing.

00:50:48.155 --> 00:50:50.530
I think we need to keep asking
those really uncomfortable

00:50:50.530 --> 00:50:55.800
questions, yeah, and be aware
of it, Look, I don't know.

00:50:55.800 --> 00:50:57.400
This is where I am.

00:50:57.400 --> 00:51:00.540
This is the battle really.

00:51:00.540 --> 00:51:03.600
Let's keep fighting
against that blindness.

00:51:03.600 --> 00:51:06.690
We have surrendered an
awfully big part of our brains

00:51:06.690 --> 00:51:08.090
to organizations.

00:51:08.090 --> 00:51:11.930
And it used to be the case
that you knew-- you know,

00:51:11.930 --> 00:51:14.430
a friend of mine who used
to live under communism,

00:51:14.430 --> 00:51:16.650
would say, under
communism, the great thing

00:51:16.650 --> 00:51:18.880
was we knew it was all
wrong in the media.

00:51:18.880 --> 00:51:20.160
So we thought quite hard.

00:51:20.160 --> 00:51:22.427
The problem is nowadays
people think it's right.

00:51:22.427 --> 00:51:23.760
And so they've stopped thinking.

00:51:23.760 --> 00:51:25.027
That's the problem.

00:51:25.027 --> 00:51:25.860
Thank you very much.

00:51:25.860 --> 00:51:26.526
AUDIENCE: Great.

00:51:26.526 --> 00:51:27.060
Thank you.

